snippet.title: Taylor Swift - "Anti-Hero" Rock Version
snippet.description:
Taylor Swift - "Anti-Hero" Rock Version

All tracks and instruments (except the vocals) were recorded and produced by me. Vocals by Taylor Swift.

Here’s the gear I use:

DAW: Studio One 6 Professional

Mixing Plugins: Slate Digital, Izotope, Valhalla Room

Mastering: Landr

Guitars: Ibanez Ghostrider

Guitar FX: Amplitube 5 Max, Guitar Rig 5, Positive Grid Bias FX 2 and Bias Amp 2

Bass: EZBass (Toontrack)

Bass FX: Amplitube 5

Drums: Superior Drummer 3 (Toontrack)

Cinematic Studio Strings
Spitfire Abbey Road One
Audio Imperia Nucleus Lite
Heavyocity Damage 2

Synths: Output (Signal, Substance, Analog Strings, Exhale, Arcade)
